### Get Dashboard Stats (Replace YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN with token from login)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Search Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users?search=test&user_type=adventurer
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Get Specific User Details
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Create New User (Admin Panel)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "username": "newuser123",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "user_type": "adventurer",
  "full_name": "New User",
  "field_of_interest": "Programming Skills",
  "commitment_level": "1_hour",
  "experience_level": "beginner"
}

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_username",
  "is_active": true
}

### Toggle User Status
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1/toggle-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Get All Quests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/quests?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Get Admin Logs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Get Admin Logs by Action Type
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/logs?action_type=DELETE_USER
